<%= content_for :stylesheet do %>
<style>
h1 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 4.5em;
    margin-top: 12px;
}

h2 {
    margin-top: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.overview {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.5em;
}

.more {
    margin-top: 12px;
}

.main .top {
    height: 18px;
    background: url(<%= asset_path 'content-bg-710-top.png' %>);
}

.main .bottom {
    height: 18px;
    background: url(<%= asset_path 'content-bg-710-bottom.png' %>);
}

.main .content {
    background: url(<%= asset_path 'content-bg-710-middle.png' %>) repeat-y;
    padding: 18px 40px;
}

.button {
    margin-top: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    height: 116px;
}

.read { background-image: url(<%= asset_path 'read-button.png' %>); }
.donate { background-image: url(<%= asset_path 'donate-button.png' %>); }
</style>
<% end %>

<h1>Free Objectivist Books for Students</h1>

<p class="overview">Get any Ayn Rand novel or book about Objectivism for free. You just have to pledge to read it.</p>

<div class="main prefix_3 grid_18">
    <div class="top">&nbsp;</div>
    <div class="content">
        <img class="alpha grid_7" src="http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/5139Z9VGNGL.jpg">
        <img class="prefix_2 grid_7 omega" src="http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51Y2mOswJIL.jpg">

        <%= link_to signup_read_path, class: "alpha grid_7" do %><div class="read button"></div><% end %>
        <%= link_to signup_donate_path, class: "prefix_2 grid_7 omega" do %><div class="donate button"></div><% end %>

        <p class="alpha grid_7 detail">Simply pledge to read <%= title "Atlas Shrugged" %>,
            <%= title "The Fountainhead" %>, or any other Objectivist book. We'll find you a donor who
            will send you the book for free. <%= link_to 'Sign up now', signup_read_path %>
        </p>
        <p class="prefix_2 grid_7 omega detail">Want to give the gift of Objectivism to eager students? A few minutes and a few
            dollars could put a book by Ayn Rand in the hands of a student who will read it.
            <%= link_to 'Sign up to donate', signup_donate_path %>
        </p>

        <div class="clear"></div>

        <h2>Questions? <%= link_to 'Read our FAQ', about_path %></h2>

        <% if !@current_user %>
        <h2>Already signed up? <%= link_to 'Log in', login_path %></h2>

        <% if session[:seen_signup] %>
        <h2>Don't want to sign up?</h2>
        <p>That's alright. Please tell me why.
            <%= mail_to 'jason@rationalegoist.com', 'Send feedback to Jason', subject: "Feedback on Free Objectivist Books" %>
        </p>
        <% end %>
        <% end %>

        <h2>What recipients are saying</h2>

        <div class="thankyou">
            <div class="alpha grid_2"><%= image_tag "poojas.png" %></div>
            <div class="grid_14 omega">
                <p class="text">I have been an avid Rand enthusiast, ever since I read Atlas Shrugged at the age of
                    fifteen. It changed my life, and since then, I've pushed myself as never before. ... I am incredibly
                    excited to read this book, further my understanding of a wonderful philosophy, and better know myself
                    in the process. Thank you, again, for making that possible for me.
                </p>
                <p class="attribution">Pooja S., Stanford University</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <%= image_tag "hr.png", class: "hr alpha grid_16 omega" %>

        <div class="thankyou">
            <div class="alpha grid_2"><%= image_tag "danielk.png" %></div>
            <div class="grid_14 omega">
                <p class="text">I can't describe how great I think it is what you do&mdash;giving away Objectivist books
                    so that people will get to know (more of) Objectivism. ... When I see people like you, doing such
                    things, it kind of gives me hope for my future&mdash;hope more like motivation, based on the few great
                    things people have done for me. I don't think I can thank you enough in an email but, I believe, you
                    have your selfish benefit from this giveaway, too. So Thank You!
                </p>
                <p class="attribution">Daniel K., Pernik, Bulgaria</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="clear"></div>

        <p class="more"><%= link_to 'More testimonials...', testimonials_path %></p>
    </div>
    <div class="bottom">&nbsp;</div>
</div>
